# Red Cube Material
# Created for POC Engine - Multi-renderable demo

newmtl RedCubeMaterial
# Ambient color (Ka) - dark red
Ka 0.4 0.05 0.05
# Diffuse color (Kd) - vibrant red
Kd 1.0 0.1 0.1
# Specular color (Ks) - white highlights
Ks 1.0 1.0 1.0
# Specular exponent (Ns) - shininess
Ns 64.0
# Optical density/Index of refraction (Ni)
Ni 1.0
# Transparency (d) - 1.0 = opaque, 0.0 = transparent
d 1.0
# Illumination model (illum)
# 2 = highlight on, ambient on, diffuse on
illum 2